'''Feather ferns''' were [[Plant/Legends|plants]] that grew on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]]. Its tall, lacy fronds could reach two to three [[Meter/Legends|meters]] in length.

The ferns grew among the exotic (and mostly predatory) flora and fauna of [[Gardulla Besadii the Elder/Legends|Gardulla the Hutt's]] [[Gardulla's pleasure garden|pleasure garden]] in her [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] [[Gardulla the Hutt's Palace/Legends|palace]], near the [[Dune Sea/Legends|Dune Sea]].

